Sasol Makes ‘Good Progress’ in Search for New CEO; Plans June Announcement

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-08T09:28:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/sasol-makes-good-progress-in-search-for-new-ceo-plans-june-announcement.html
  Sasol Ltd. (SOL)  is making “good
progress” in its search for a replacement for Chief Executive
Officer Pat Davies, who “reaches the normal retirement age”
for Sasol executives in March.  The company aims to make a further announcement by the end
of June, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
